summary: The document comprises memorandums detailing the request for alias documentation and a backstopped driver's license for Harold F. Swenson, as part of the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992. It highlights the collaboration between the Technical Services Division and the Office of Security to facilitate this process for operational needs.
key_findings: Request for alias documentation and a backstopped driver's license for Harold F. Swenson.
Collaboration between the Technical Services Division and the Office of Security in processing the request.
Documentation released under the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992.
Operational activities necessitating the use of alias documentation.
keywords: President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992
